Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 跑哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭也没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小肥 小肥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不想待了 这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(658,385)\3c&H000000&\shad0\bord2\be3}「神社与寺庙」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年是不是干梅雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带树木很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是寺庙哦 春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺庙？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是臭小子说要去看石狮子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉 银太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 也顺便可以带悟逛逛城镇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌麻烦就在家里躺着呗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也那么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你慢死了 快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这声音在哪听过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.46,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了 好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将平同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 好大的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有 破旧不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才是和由美打电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说对了 她说她现在要过来看小肥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们关系真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小真才是 你男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是有来往的神社家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸红个什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 其他人看不见小春和银太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是看在眼里的就是我们俩单独在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天本 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说和我们不是一个学校 他是由美的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 刚才的停顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 冴木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这做什么呀 连神尾也在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 只是带悟逛逛城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 去看看小咪的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧 来来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺庙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 银太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是带礼物来 真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小将 由美来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 还有不认识的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的朋友 冴木和神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎 我是将平的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他姐姐藤野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是菊里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 初次见面 我是冴木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 藤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有个非常可爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 小将 你还有这样的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级正统帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真叫人烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 芹香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹香小姐 车子洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天陪我去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来还要修整下庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事晚点再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不行 我正在修行途中…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是好男人 绝对要擒到手来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热热闹闹的叫人羡慕才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家就我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不想住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 头发该扒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来看小肥的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将平真不容易啊 各种方面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪你怎么了 躲在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美 内裤会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 这次我一定要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 冷静下来 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你家这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啥 其实我家有东西出没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西是指鬼怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 寺庙嘛 没啥好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前可没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很平常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会编胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.56,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.84,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你没欺负小咪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:08.76,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没欺负它…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点想回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说出没 但也并不是就能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经习惯了就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打坐时有东西倒下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有风 蜡烛却自个熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修整好的庭院被弄得乱糟糟的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸都说「这也是佛门修行之一」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非小肥是看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为佛事没做够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.66,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么会出现鬼怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.37,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 寺庙和神社不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里沉眠着很多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银太郎大人 你察觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 微微感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这不是神社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 这里明明是寺庙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这很久以前就在院落内了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是我家在管理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺庙里有神社不是很常见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小真你很在意吗 不愧是神社家孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前神明和佛祖都是交织在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么好稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神佛调和的余音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们随便看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 什么又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银太郎 难道说这么小的神社里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和神社大小没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 我们也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使又没什么稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉最近这事特别多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西都能倒下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哦 小吹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗噗 小吹 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人呆呆的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是啊 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类竟然看得到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个奇怪的小不点是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 还有个大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们俩 给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁小不点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 银 他们都被吓着了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是还什么都没做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为他们这么说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是神使吧 没和人类说过话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔你也是神使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们完全不一样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呀 是猴子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 就像爷爷之前说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我们以外还有很多各种各样的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了没 至今为止的骚动都是这俩干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好像也没人能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了吧 咱们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那怎么行 既然如此得提醒他们别再恶作剧了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是外人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多管闲事为好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你自己留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看见小风吗 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 「可爱可爱」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类中的女性总是立马就会这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风就顾自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 小吹 可爱吗可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快从悟身上滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么啊这蝴蝶结 真嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春的蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银太郎 快给我抓住这只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后好好教训教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论年纪 小春还算是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你们 适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服气的话 就过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打屁股 打屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没那本事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出门就不会遇到什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管神使还是人类 小孩子都一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 真琴 赶紧完事回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 大叔你好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上 银太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住好好教训他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也别说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你们适可而止点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 讨厌 你们正忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了 哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天过的 什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 刚就是佛事用具倒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 将平 找不到小咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是到墓地那块去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 银太郎 快抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉无所谓了 你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 那个拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 是风刮的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚯 还能起风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这看来 可是能随心所欲到处恶作剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的风 是那俩孩子刮的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 人类能看见的话好难恶作剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙好碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 神使才不会做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶作剧可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我们忘掉烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你们不是要来抓我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大叔你扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春才没那么闲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手住手 你耍诈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来抓我们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 受够了 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 多事大笨女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.48,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你做这种小学生做的事要做到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 悟 那俩孩子为什么要恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是因为他们觉得好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们才没考虑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恶作剧导致别人吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致别人以为是鬼怪而害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是神使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生在小春你身上 你也不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不愿意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是寺庙 没人能看见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们又是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为与人类的关系太疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问问住持大师吧 或许能知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:16:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座神社现在是由我们家在管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是早在建寺之前就在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们家寺庙占用了这座神社的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前这一带 经常会有猴子下山来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座神社的神使是神猿 想必也是因为如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神佛分离的那段时期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为寺庙较大而且神社又没人照料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这样留在了院落内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 寺庙能发展成现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也要多亏这座神社的保佑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子可是必胜的象征啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明之猴 读作神猿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 和佛祖一样 都是我们应该感恩的神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去墓地那边找找小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前还有很多猴子来这里玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为太孤单了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为想赶走人类才恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有很多同伴在 明明过得很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却因为寺庙的建立导致猴子们从这里消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊 神使知晓过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说没办法 他们是孩子又没人能看见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春我也有讨厌的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问问当事人如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么跑怎么跑都立刻就被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不能告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 赶走人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从来没这么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么还要恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 很沉闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来寺庙的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在哭泣 都很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我们也会跟着伤感的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想稍微吓吓他们 让他们忘记忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 爷爷也说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前这里的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说现已不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风 吹 就算同伴们不来了 但也无需哀叹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是换成了人类罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说随着人类增多会发生很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们只要笑容以对就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是胜利象征的神猿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不笑容满面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就谁都不能获得胜利的喜悦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们觉得应该快乐至上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 这里有寺庙 也有墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们活的很久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要连同人类 同伴以及爷爷的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在以后的日子里 也要一直默默守护这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 恶作剧或许是过了点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你们以你们的方式鼓舞了大家不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类也都有能够自己排忧解难的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别再恶作剧也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那多没意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为吓吓人类好有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最大的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 猴类的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 冴木你真的很喜欢超自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很可爱啊 神明大人的恶作剧什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真吉利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好吗 一两只猴灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家与之相似的也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在佛祖之余 还能得到神明的佑护真叫人感激涕零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真对那些家伙不放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许应该偶尔来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们又没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将平他们家人也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使的事情 他们怎么可能会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不相信也没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定就是作为沟通双方的桥梁而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风和小吹完全不拘泥于神社或者寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的神明大人真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也没有比日本的神明大人更随心所欲的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该说这是心胸宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为神明大人使者的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅有狐狸 还有猴子 兔子 乌龟 乌鸦等等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着很多很多各种各样的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.13,0:24:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿神明保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:55.79,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私の生まれた　この場所この部屋で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.86,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}出会ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:06.34,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}古ぼけたランプは　今も優しい光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.16,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ずっと昔から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:21.65,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}紡がれてきた時間を 気付かせてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.71,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}胸に灯そう　心の中のランプ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:32.47,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今隠れてた絆照らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:38.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私にそっと　囁きかけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.10,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Ah 「僕はいつもここだよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:50.50,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}差し伸べた手ほら　繋いだら君に言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.10,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}言葉は　「君を信じているから…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:01.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}この手を離さないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:55.79,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在这里  我出生的这间小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.86,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}与你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:06.34,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那盏披满灰尘的老煤油灯  现在依旧摇曳着温暖的微光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}点亮我的心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.16,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}让我回忆起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:21.65,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那段懵懂间悄然编织的青葱岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.71,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那心灵的明灯  请照亮我的胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:32.47,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如今也点亮了那深埋心底的丝丝羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:38.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}请悄悄地于我耳畔细语呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.10,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Ah 「我一直陪伴在你身旁」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:50.50,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}伸出双手 如果触碰到你就可以对你诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.10,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那不变的话语 「因为相信你…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:01.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}请不要松开我的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.98,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}遠く聞こえてる　人の聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.44,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}振り返り　ほくそ笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.69,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一から百になる刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:04.29,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その一瞬が　永遠だね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:15.21,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}孤獨さえ支配したいと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:26.29,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}疑心暗鬼　敵わないや　手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:38.45,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界の始まりは偽りの物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:45.35,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月がそっと笑ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.96,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}なゆたの未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:55.65,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}繋ぐメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:24:08.37,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕を空へ導いてくれるSTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.98,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}远处传来的 谁的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.44,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}回过头去 暗自嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.69,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}从一到百那霎那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:04.29,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}也将是永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:15.21,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}原以为自己可以支配孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:26.29,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}但却疑心暗鬼 果然敌不过 索性伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:38.45,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界的起始是个虚伪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:45.35,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月亮不禁一旁窃笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.96,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}这或许是连接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:55.65,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那无尽岁月未来的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:24:08.37,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}指引我飞上天空的STORY
